{"tid":1860981,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"林鄭：不符使用要求的官員不准戴口罩","createTime":"2020-02-04T02:57:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-04T05:28:19.000Z","uid":20933,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"f447da2abc23bf599d943e970188ba732c271fb7","tid":1860981,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T02:57:01.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】行政長官林鄭月娥表示，已下令不符使用要求的官員不准戴口罩。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥出席行政會議前表示，全球口罩供應緊張，在內地採購不成功，需要謹慎使用口罩；而參考世衛1月29日指引、其他地方的安排及內部意見，認為有空間減少使用口罩。她已向部門發出指引，生病、負責前線服務及到人多密集地方的員工，才應使用口罩。<br />\n<br />\n她又說，若官員並非患病等理由，要求他們不准佩戴口罩。"},{"pid":"5f455bc3a376fa4592e826d63792355ff6103a08","tid":1860981,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T02:57:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/editorsChoice/player?newsId=379243\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2FeditorsChoice%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D379243&d=oexceJgjEuhZ1NUs%2FbcNdPDXWQKahOldmH8%2Bpia8yKE%3D&h=d942100f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2FeditorsChoice%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D379243&h=a966e305\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/editorsChoice/player?newsId=379243</a>"},{"pid":"b367a69b101a64a8ddc59d1f5ab3cb5445a8fe4c","tid":1860981,"uid":158613,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T03:01:07.000Z","msg":"淋巴癌上腦"},{"pid":"887e65a156f696a608039552b2c6e4072575a20a","tid":1860981,"uid":123774,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T03:01:30.000Z","msg":"癡撚咗線"},{"pid":"17cc81cf32eb25b0020b97548a22d6f295ea5a2a","tid":1860981,"uid":46148,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T03:06:01.000Z","msg":"係機會<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一個武漢撚就可以收佢皮加冚家產"},{"pid":"253c95f2afff17bf862b0fbb15d66df93f6de40c","tid":1860981,"uid":14103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T03:16:54.000Z